.TH man 1 "@BUILD_DATE@" "@PACKAGE_VERSION@" "flom man page"
.SH NAME
flom \- serialize a command execution
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "flom"
[OPTION] -- [COMMAND [ARG]...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run COMMAND serializing it with other commands executed by flom.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP 4
.B "-h, --help"
show help options
.TP
.B -t, --trace-file=\fIFILENAME
specify daemon trace filename (FILENAME must be an absolute path)
.TP
.B -v, --version
print flom version and exit
.SH CAVEATS
.B flom -- flom --
[COMMAND [ARG]...]
.P
hangs due to a deadlock: the inner flom instance waits the lock obtained by the first flom instance.
